1.0.name: wordpress/sn-facebook-like
1.0.description:
SN Facebook Like - Facebook Like Box or Like Button with advanced slider (retioSlider). You can select some settings for slider like: 1. Box position ( left, right, top, bottom ), 1. Slider action ( hover, click ), 1. Open / close time ( in ms ) 1. Start / open / close opacity of SN Facebook Like box 1. Chose 1 of 15 unique icons.

SN Facebook Like require jQuery 1.4+
